<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> أَرْكَانُهُ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> الزَّوْجَانِ الخَالِيَانِ عَنِ المَوَانِعِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَإِيجَابٌ بِلَفْظِ: <span class="c1">"أَنَكَحْتُ"</span>، أَوْ <span class="c1">"زَوَّجْتُ"</span>،<span class="c5"> وَقَبُولٌ بِلَفْظِ:</span> <span class="c1">"قَبِلْتُ"</span>، أَوْ <span class="c1">"رَضِيتُ"</span> فَقَطْ، أَوْ مَعَ <span class="c1">"هَذَا النِّكَاحِ"</span>، أَوْ <span class="c1">"تَزَوَّجْتُهَا"</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَمَنْ جَهِلَهُمَا:</span> لَمْ يَلْزَمْهُ تَعَلُّمٌ، وَكَفَاهُ مَعْنَاهُمَا الخَاصُّ بِكُلِّ لِسَانٍ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرُوطُهُ أَرْبَعَةٌ:</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> تَعْيِينُ الزَّوْجَيْنِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَرِضَاهُمَا.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>-<span class="c5"> لَكِنْ لِأَبٍ وَوَصِيِّهِ فِي نِكَاحٍ تَزْوِيجُ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c2">(١)</span> صَغِيرٍ.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(٢)</span> وَبَالِغٍ مَعْتُوهٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(٣)</span> وَمَجْنُونَةٍ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٤)</span> وَثَيِّبٍ لَهَا دُونَ تِسْعٍ.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>